apache server :

if apache didnt come with the ubuntu :
sudo apt install apache2

sudo service apache2 restart
sudo systemctl enable apache - for startup on system startup

-------
a2enmod proxy
a2enmod proxy_http
------

substitute : systemctl reload apache2
-------

ssl in apache :
reason : so that ssl doesnt have to be implemented in each apps and doesnt have to be run by each app at run time

